---
title: Easy Lemon Pepper Chicken with Sesame Potato Chunks & Crumbly Cheese Salad
description: This lemon pepper spiced chicken is a simple combination that has been tried-and-tested and never fails to
deliver a tender and flavoursome result. Served alongside sesame-roasted potatoes, this dish is sure to be a hit.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
